(39, 0, '<div class="prodview_prices" style="padding:0px;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	音叉料位计已经广泛用于工业现场，单棒振动式料位开关又是音叉料位开关的其中一种，它不怕挂料不怕冲击，没有夹料问题，而且灵敏度高。它的圆柱形单根探测杆结构决定了它对工业现场更广泛的适应性。它运用音叉“共振”原理，在压电元件的驱动下产生振动，只有探杆周围全部被物料包围时，振幅才会急剧减少，从而产生开关动作。适用于低密度的粉/液体状态检测。\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="prodview_content" style="padding:8px 15px 0px;margin:0px;text-align:justify;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<p align="center">\r\n		<img alt="" src="http://www.wolsn.com/upload/image/20130913220251_25114.png" width="273" height="353" />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p align="left">\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">一、概述</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">音叉料位计已经广泛用于工业现场，单棒振动式料位开关又是音叉料位开关的其中一种，它不怕挂料不怕冲击，没有夹料问题，而且灵敏度高。它的圆柱形单根探测杆结构决定了它对工业现场更广泛的适应性。它运用音叉</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">“</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">共振</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">原理，在压电元件的驱动下产生振动，只有探杆周围全部被物料包围时，振幅才会急剧减少，从而产生开关动作。适用于低密度的粉</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">液体状态检测。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:24pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">二、特性</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">物体与感应棒相接触并有阻尼时，提供延迟输出。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">高低故障保险模式。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">灵敏度可调，能够检测极低密度粉料。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">易使用，坚固耐用。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">与音叉先比，无叉体的安装问题，不受夹料影响。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">与阻旋相比，无可动部件，坚固的探头耐磨损和物料冲击，灵敏度可调。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">与电容式相比，不受介电系数的影响，表面自清洁。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">安装后无需校准。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">外壳防护等级可达</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">IP65</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，可户外安装。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">三、应用</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">输送设备料流检测。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">固液界面检测。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">粉体、颗粒料、块状固体料位检测。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:21pt;text-indent:-21pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">四、技术规格</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">电&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 源：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">AC85</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">～</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">265V</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">（另可选</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">11</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">～</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">33V DC</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">）</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">功&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 率：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">2.5W</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">振动频率：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">400Hz</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">继电器触点：常开常闭接点</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;AC250V/DC30V</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">5A</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">阻性负载</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">电气连接：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">M20</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">×</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">1.5(</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">￠</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">～￠</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">14</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">电缆</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">)</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">材质：外壳</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">压铸铝</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">振动杆</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">/304</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">不锈钢</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">外壳防护：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">IP65</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">最大压力：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">1.6MPa</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">松密度：高灵敏度用于细粉末（松密度</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">0.3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">～</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">0.5g/cm</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">）</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">输出延时时间：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">0</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">～</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">秒可调</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">起&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 振：&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">秒</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">工作温度：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;-10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">～</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">85</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">℃</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">连接螺纹：&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">寸</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">NPT</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">寸）或法兰连接</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">信号指示：&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">个发光二极管</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">LED</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">提供调控、输出和电源</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">可调电位器：&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">件，调节延时和灵敏度</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;">可调开关：&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">个</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">DIP</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">开关用于时间延时选择、高</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">/</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">低失效保护</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;<b><span style="font-family:宋体;">安装注意要点：</span></b><b><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、安装时注意安装位置，接线盒的出线口必须朝下，且电缆固定头必须锁紧以防止下雨时雨水由出线口渗入接线盒内，破坏内部的结构及线路。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、多支感应棒同时安装时，各开关之间应保持</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">300mm</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">以上的距离。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、应避免安装在靠近入料口，以减少加料时冲击损坏感应棒。若开关必须靠近入料口安装，请在开关上方</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">200mm</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">处加装一块保护角钢。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:18pt;text-indent:-18pt;">\r\n		<span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、推荐倾斜式安装。感应棒向下倾斜并与水平线保持</span><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">20</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">度夹角为最佳。如此可增加灵敏度，并减少下料冲击造成开关损坏。</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="MsoNormal">\r\n		<span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">、料仓内感应棒不能当梯子踩