fy;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">4、全机械结构，密封性好，故障率低</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="padding:0px;margin:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">5、抗地震性能好</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.wolsn.com/upload/image/20130921144631_41651.png" width="406" height="224" style="height:267px;width:543px;" />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;background-color:#FFFFFF;"></span>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.wolsn.com/upload/image/20130921144707_68425.png" width="612" height="155" />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;background-color:#FFFFFF;"></span>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:18px;">&nbsp;吹气/扫工作原理图例：</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://www.wolsn.com/upload/image/20130921145054_13224.png" width="548" height="277" />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;background-color:#FFFFFF;"></span>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:Arial, ����, Helvetica, sans-serif, Verdana;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;fon